subject: connectors
msgSnippet: Chuck: I have never seen such an annoying site as this stupid Yahoogroups.  Due to a change in my e-mail address necessitated by my ISP I have been struggling
messageBody:
Chuck:

I have never seen such an annoying site as this stupid Yahoogroups. Due
to a change in my e-mail address necessitated by my ISP I have been
struggling for 1/2 hour to send a reply to your message, but the site
keeps changing the addressee and then telling me it can't deliver the
e-mail.

Since I cannot copy the original e-mail, I will condense it.

In my humble opinion, no connectors should be used unless authorized by
the QS manual. Kingsley Read knew what he was doing.

The original was more diplomatic, but I have run out of patience.

Paige Gabhart
